    <section class="about-section padding-large">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="image-holder">
              <img src="{{ asset('images/about-image.jpg') }}" alt="about us" class="img-fluid">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="about-content">
              <h2 class="display-5 text-uppercase text-dark mb-4">Our Story</h2>
              <p>Founded in 2010, Ministore began as a small tech shop with a big vision. We started with a simple idea: to provide high-quality tech products with exceptional customer service at reasonable prices.</p>
              <p>Over the years, we've grown from a single store to a nationwide retailer with an extensive online presence. Our commitment to quality and customer satisfaction has remained unwavering throughout our journey.</p>
              <p>Today, we offer a wide range of products from smartphones and smartwatches to accessories and audio equipment. We carefully select each item in our inventory to ensure it meets our high standards of quality and performance.</p>
              <a href="{{ path('app_shop') }}" class="btn btn-medium btn-dark text-uppercase btn-rounded-none mt-3">Shop Now</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

